<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Email Verification</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@200..800&family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: "Manrope", sans-serif;
            color: #333333;
        }

        body {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 0;
            max-width: 580px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .email-header {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .email-header img {
            width: 40px;
            height: auto;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .email-header .title {
            font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
        }

        .email-content {
            padding: 30px 20px;
            background: white;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .message {
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .user-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .user-details p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .user-details strong {
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: block;
            background-color: #546eee;
            color: white !important;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #4a62d6;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .note {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #777;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .signature {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .signature p {
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        .email-footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .email-footer img {
            width: 40px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .email-footer p {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        .email-footer a {
            color: #546eee;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .email-footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .copyright {
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #999;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <img src="cid:logoImage" alt="Mysertifico Logo" />
            <div class="title">MySertifico</div>
        </div>

        <div class="email-content">
            <div class="greeting">Salam sejahtera, <%= name %>!</div>
            <div class="message">Sila klik butang di bawah untuk reset password</div>

            <a href="<%= link %>" class="cta-button">Reset Password</a>

            <div class="user-details">
                <p>Berikut adalah butiran akaun anda:</p>
                <p><strong>Nama:</strong> <%= name %></p>
                <p><strong>E-mel:</strong> <%= email %></p>
            </div>


            <div class="signature">
                <p><strong>Salam hormat,</strong></p>
                <p>MySertifico</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="email-footer">
            <img src="cid:logoImage" alt="MySertifico Logo" />
            <p>Perlukan bantuan? Hubungi +6019 489 2806 atau hantarkan mesej melalui e-mel</p>
            <a href="mailto:support@mpsonline.my">support@mysertificoonline.my</a>
            <div class="copyright">
                <p>Hak Cipta Terpelihara Â© 2025 Webapp Studiohub Sdn. Bhd.</p>
                <p>Hak cipta dilindungi undang-undang.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
